{"tid":770011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"二宮和也 定 木村 😊","createTime":"2018-08-06T16:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T05:03:16.000Z","uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d82d8c61b7239dc40c51dc43db037e1d7b15ee17","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://contents.oricon.co.jp/upimg/news/20180806/2117034_201808060140982001533567560c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.oricon.co.jp%2Fupimg%2Fnews%2F20180806%2F2117034_201808060140982001533567560c.jpg&h=789fb2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似唔似父子？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e19c367b92fff27ee7bf331f9101d2f735864cd","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"木村老左好多，唔講以為五十出頭？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5b834d05c92b5f2bd7ed66a5cff2397d65c5cc9","tid":770011,"uid":88491,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"木村已經好矮，隔離果個幾高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1427f37679646834ed7fc1956769601027aa987","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>木村已經好矮，隔離果個幾高？</blockquote><br />\n出道時好似168<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08ef2d14397d939c6342b6528bc68c438ddd698a","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nikkansports.com/entertainment/news/img/201808060000662-w500_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikkansports.com%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2Fimg%2F201808060000662-w500_0.jpg&h=ba98e704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f1b4dec91b26cc17e4be2147ea8c49c60a54be","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"只係相差10年<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-08-06 <br />\n<br />\n木村拓哉（45）と嵐・二宮和也（35）の初共演が話題の映画『検察側の罪人』（24日公開）の完成披露試写会が6日、都内で開催された。上映前には4000人の観客の前で、木村、二宮、原田眞人監督（69）らが舞台あいさつを行い、見どころをアピールした。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2117034/full/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oricon.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2117034%2Ffull%2F&d=E5UWrIDhKMu6tZp4Qm1do8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a4c7be66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2117034/full/</a>"},{"pid":"f37d445e2062d3516ea3b2483d0341683e771c30","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"類似的「身高詐欺」，在日本藝壇其實也不遑多讓，官方提供的身高數字其實大多僅供參考。<br />\n<br />\n像傑尼斯事務所就老早被公認是最大的身高灌水偶像製造廠，J家藝人的身高浮報個 2~3 公分根本不是新鮮事，想與他們合作拍戲的女星身高都不能太高，免得讓偶像在螢光幕前漏氣。其中，最為人津津樂道，早就被日本鄉民戲稱作「都市傳說」的，就是日劇天王木村拓哉謎樣的身高了吧。<br />\n<br />\n早年基本資料上，<span style=\"color: red;\">木村身高為 176 公分，但不斷有人爆料天王真實身高根本不到 170 公分，甚至是僅有 163 公分高，說他是靠特製的增高靴和刻意吹高的頭髮來混淆視聽「增高」，與他合作的女星身高都有嚴格限制</span>。唯獨五年前 174 公分的林志玲跨海破案，打破這不成文規矩，與木村合演《月之戀人》，雖然當時她在戲裡多以平底鞋現身，許多鏡頭也刻意錯位，或是坐著拍，兩人顯得有點尷尬其實根本沒差的身高差，還是蔚為話題。前陣子他為拍攝台灣觀光宣傳短片首度來台，本以為這世紀之謎得以解開，沒想到他抵台時穿上招牌的靴子增高加上紳士帽再增高，天王到底有多高，依舊是說不清的秘密。"},{"pid":"4a014824c55378899350d6bd1c5fc0eb0e422c80","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"傑尼斯團體「嵐」的成員二宮和也，剛出道時官方身高 168 公分，但十年前他與當時身高約 166 公分的長澤雅美(現在據說長高到 168 公分了)合作演出電視劇《溫柔時光》，並肩而站看起來就是一般高。<span style=\"color: red;\">其實他幾次在演唱會或是訪問上自爆只有 167 左右</span>，公司為了數字好看才灌水。今年五月他也誠實地大方在廣播上透露定期健檢的結果，實際身高 167.8 公分，體重也只有 55 公斤。偶像嘛，不過只差一公分還是要灌點水！<br />\n<br />\n不過，話說回來，木村拓哉至今都過 40 歲，還是不少熟女嫩妹心目中的理想標準，當年二宮和也與長澤假戲真做，談了兩年的地下情，之後也傳與名模佐佐木希等人交往，戀情不斷；綾野剛也是超強發電機，與他合作女星無一不淪陷，與新垣結衣也假戲真做談戀愛，看來能不能幸福，戀情能不能萌芽，其實無謂有沒有最萌身高差，可能還是跟長相比較有關係吧!"},{"pid":"bf6ca81f9002e76b30a135c7bf418c1e4ca2b2ea","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.sponichi.co.jp/entertainment/news/2018/08/06/jpeg/20180806s00041000286000p_view.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sponichi.co.jp%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fjpeg%2F20180806s00041000286000p_view.jpg&h=fd6e3131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"324529c08184bd70e687c0c3df36628181e00976","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"d人提起木村就會諗起hero，咁提起二宮又會諗起咩？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92da2fe040899016dd154e8aa1c6082e1ddbb31b","tid":770011,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"木村可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75337e7ae70619f3ff7f4531d19f42b9df550c38","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>木村可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個女都十幾歲啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/023858_47bc6c7aa8097aa75731f8d869a8366a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F023858_47bc6c7aa8097aa75731f8d869a8366a.png&h=c116a883&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e5b6aa204fbe46ff2bea4490db8d0dbbf47a539","tid":770011,"uid":197584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"二宮和也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8499ef81891916711b7176c62ddc6ed9b31c51","tid":770011,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"324529c08184bd70e687c0c3df36628181e00976","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"d人提起木村就會諗起hero，咁提起二宮又會諗起咩？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F