0011,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/131656_5a364b8e3b2b31641bcf6068ac8d22fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F131656_5a364b8e3b2b31641bcf6068ac8d22fd.png&h=e3134f39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d7fa2933dbddbab8cc39dd0cc955aa0e8e5db4e","tid":770011,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e98c68289c2deef079c4cbdf06b5dfa79448e2b","tid":770011,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/131656_5a364b8e3b2b31641bcf6068ac8d22fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F131656_5a364b8e3b2b31641bcf6068ac8d22fd.png&h=e3134f39&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"香港月尾上"},{"pid":"67219cab9b4e18cdfe58fc861b64fc4e8d60351f","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d人提起木村就會諗起hero，咁提起二宮又會諗起咩？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>食女<br />\n長澤佐佐木希都比佢食左</blockquote><br />\n我可能表達唔好，其實係想問一提起佢會唔會諗起一套比較出名而又有佢拍既劇，即係好似木村-hero咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3260e14134b4f1ff974e2c7e55a5abef69b5efe6","tid":770011,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislik